  "title": "The Horizon: AI and Interoperability",
  "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start; padding: 5% 8%; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body);\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      position: relative;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin-bottom: 2rem;\n      text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);\n      border-left: 6px solid var(--accent);\n      padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    .bullet-container {\n      list-style: none;\n      padding: 0;\n      margin: 0;\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 800px;\n    }\n    .bullet-item {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.2vw, 1.8rem);\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .bullet-item:hover {\n      transform: translateX(10px);\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n    }\n    .bullet-item::before {\n      content: '→';\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin-right: 1rem;\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      transition: all 0.6s ease-out;\n    }\n    .reveal.visible {\n      opacity: 1;\n      transform: translateY(0);\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <h1 class=\"slide-title reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.1s\">The Horizon: AI and Interoperability</h1>\n  \n  <ul class=\"bullet-container\">\n    <li class=\"bullet-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.3s\">Integration of AI for automated DAO governance</li>\n    <li class=\"bullet-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.5s\">Cross-chain communication protocols</li>\n    <li class=\"bullet-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.7s\">Tokenization of real-world assets (RWA)</li>\n    <li class=\"bullet-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.9s\">The move toward a seamless 'Internet of Blockchains'</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  \n</section>",
